reviewText: Wubbzy is always a favorite in my house!
This DVD is wonderful if your child like Wubbzy!

This DVD contains six episodes from the Wow! Wow! Wubbzy! cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. Wubbzy and the Fire Engine
2. What Would Wubbzy Do?
3. Ty Ty the Tool Guy (with Ty Pennington from "Extreme Home Makeover")
4. Mr. Unlucky
5. Wuzzleburg Express
6. Hangin' with Mr. Gummy
My son loved this DVD for Christmas. Was one of his favorite things! We also got the Wubbzy beanie baby to go with it and he was thrilled.

A great addition to their collection! You won't go wrong with this edition. This makes 8 and counting.
Wow Wow Wubzzy is an all around great and entertaining cartoon.

Just in time for National Fire Prevention Week, which was on October 9, we got the chance to review "Wubbzy And The Fire Engine."  It is a DVD full of six Wubbzy and friends fun-filled episodes!  My boys are hooked on firefighters right now and this DVD was perfect for them.  Wubbzy is a wholesome show for preschoolers that features friendship, teamwork, decision-making, and other issues young kids may face. My boys love how fun and bright the characters are and as a parent I don't mind watching it with them!
